            <abstract id="ref45" label="Abstract">This collection contains records from the Office of the Provost Marshal, Seventh Congressional District, New York, which oversaw enlistments for the Union Army from the 11th and 17th wards of New York City. Portions of this collection relating to the Civil War have been digitized and are available to on-site researchers and to users affiliated with subscribing institutions via 
